Package me.Salt.Event.jevent.game.cardsagainstdiscord

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaDGameAddPlayerEvent
    Fired when a player is added to a Cards Against Discord game.
    CaDGameAddPreviousBlackCardEvent
    This event is fired when a black card is added to the list of previous black cards in a Cards Against Discord game.
    CaDGameRemovePlayerEvent  
    CaDGameUpdateActiveEvent
    This event is fired when a Cards Against Discord game changes its activity state.
    CaDManagerAddEmbedEvent
    This event is fired when a Cards Against Discord message is registered to the CaDGameManager.
    CaDManagerInvokeStateEvent
    This event is fired when the CaDManager invokes a specified state.
    CaDManagerModifyHandlerEvent
    This event is fired when the CaDManager modifies an existing CaDHandler instance.
    CaDManagerRegisterHandlerEvent
    This event fires when a CaDGameHandler is being registered to the CaDManager.
    GenericCaDEvent
    This event is fired when a Cards Against Discord-related event is fired.
    GenericCaDGameEvent
    This event is fired when a Cards Against Discord Game-related event is fired.
    GenericCaDManagerEvent
    This event is fired when a Cards Against Discord Manager-related event is fired.
